Maybe you can make a soup.

128
00:11:23,726 --> 00:11:25,141
- You're sick.

129
00:11:25,143 --> 00:11:27,020
How about some split pea soup?

130
00:11:27,896 --> 00:11:30,355
- That will keep us warm
tonight.

131
00:11:30,357 --> 00:11:32,482
- You know what else would keep
us warm?

132
00:11:32,484 --> 00:11:33,360
A fire!

133
