trouble.

171
00:16:11,013 --> 00:16:12,638
We don't need men.

172
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:15,015
I mean, we're already
playing hooky anyway.

173
00:16:15,017 --> 00:16:16,850
- Ugh, you're right.

174
00:16:16,852 --> 00:16:18,727
