journal.

183
00:16:39,499 --> 00:16:41,332
"I've been trying to recall the
days.

184
00:16:41,334 --> 00:16:43,043
"The nights feel eternal.

185
00:16:43,045 --> 00:16:44,795
"As I fail to know the
improvements

186
00:16:44,797 --> 00:16:46,379
"I've made in the poor girl,

187
00:16:46,381 --> 00:16:49,550
"the convulsions only
worsen a withering soul.

188
00:16:49,552 --> 00:16:51,635
"Only more sickened by the
surroundings

189
00:16:51,637 --> 00:16:55,140
"and the perhaps ill will
of her strange mother."

190
00:16:59,770 --> 00:17:02,729
