of the Lord Jesus Christ.

206
00:17:53,198 --> 00:17:55,991
But Mary, she's troubling me.

207
00:17:55,993 --> 00:17:58,537
Always walking around
town like a common tart.

208
00:17:59,454 --> 00:18:01,246
I wonder where she learned that
from?

209
00:18:01,248 --> 00:18:05,542
- Are you referring to
me?

210
00:18:05,544 --> 00:18:09,170
- And always making a
mockery during the mass,

211
00:18:09,172 --> 00:18:12,549
yawning incessantly when I give
the homily

212
00:18:12,551 --> 00:18:15,971
and when I lift up the Holy
Eucharist, incessant giggles.

213
00:18:16,805 --> 00:18:17,804
